title: Fall Guys Breaks Insane Records - Kinda Funny Games Daily 08.26.20
description:
Tim and Gary sit down for Whitta Wednesday to talk Nintendo Direct, Fall Guys breaking records, Perfect Dark rumors, and more. 

Time Stamps - 
 00:00:00 - Start
00:02:00 - Housekeeping
Our first Impressions of Mafia Definitive Edition are live
Gamescom Opening Night Live is happening THIS Thursday. You can catch us reacting to it live right here on Twitch.tv/KindaFunnyGames right after Thursday’s KFGD. It’ll be your regular reacts crew.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Mohammed Mohammed & Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:12:00 - Fall Guys Is the Most Downloaded PS Plus Game Ever - Devolver Digital’s Twitter
00:20:50 - September’s PS Plus Games Revealed from PlayStation Blog
00:22:55 - Nintendo Direct Mini: Partner Showcase (Roundup by IGN’s Adam Bankhurst)
00:35:14 - JeffGrub Perfect Dark Rumors
00:44:50 - Wasteland 3 Early Reviews are In!
00:53:30 - Out today
 Reader mail   -
00:55:50 - Just a dumb thought but as we are on the edge of making games at 4k/60fps.... is this it - Use the Breaks
01:04:30 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Blessing& Imran
